      <title>泽连斯基称俄罗斯已被哈尔科夫防线第一线阻截</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/russia-halted-by-first-line-of-kharkiv-s-defense-zelenskiy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·泽伦斯基表示，俄罗斯上周对乌克兰东北部新战线的攻击最远达10公里（6.2英里），随后被基辅在哈尔科夫地区的第一道防线阻止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/russia-halted-by-first-line-of-kharkiv-s-defense-zelenskiy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 07:05:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在猛烈攻击武器后发射导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/north-korea-appears-to-test-fire-ballistic-missile-south-korea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜向其东海岸海域发射了一枚疑似弹道导弹。几个小时前，朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹直言不讳地斥责有关朝鲜向俄罗斯出口武器的指控是“虚构的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/north-korea-appears-to-test-fire-ballistic-missile-south-korea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 06:26:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国致力于重新控制新喀里多尼亚部分地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/france-has-lost-control-of-parts-of-new-caledonia-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高级专员路易斯·勒弗朗表示，法国政府正在采取行动，重新控制太平洋领土新喀里多尼亚，安全部队抵达该群岛，结束支持独立团体一周的暴力抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/france-has-lost-control-of-parts-of-new-caledonia-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 05:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在降低美国关税方面宣扬经济韧性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/china-touts-economic-resilience-in-mitigating-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家统计局发言人表示，中国强劲的经济和多元化的贸易伙伴将有助于减轻美国额外关税的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/china-touts-economic-resilience-in-mitigating-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 04:52:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
