      <title>普京探究弱点，而泽伦斯基则填补防御漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/putin-attacks-kharkiv-as-ukraine-scrambles-to-plug-vulnerable-defenses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在乌克兰东北部持续一周的攻势给基辅敲响了警钟，总统泽伦斯基和他的将军们急忙加强防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/putin-attacks-kharkiv-as-ukraine-scrambles-to-plug-vulnerable-defenses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩直言不讳的妹妹猛烈抨击美国针对贸易而出口武器的指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/kim-jong-un-s-outspoken-sister-blasts-claims-of-arms-exports-as-us-targets-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对武器贸易实施新制裁后不久，朝鲜领导人直言不讳的妹妹就指责朝鲜向俄罗斯出口武器的指控是“虚构的”。华盛顿称，武器贸易为克里姆林宫袭击乌克兰提供了动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/kim-jong-un-s-outspoken-sister-blasts-claims-of-arms-exports-as-us-targets-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 01:11:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南中央政治局委员因违反党规​​辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/vietnam-politburo-member-resigns-over-party-damaging-violations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南共产党批准了政治局委员张氏梅的辞职，这使她成为自 2022 年以来在腐败调查不断扩大的情况下第六位下台的政治局官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/vietnam-politburo-member-resigns-over-party-damaging-violations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 11:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
